{"tid":1127690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國會議長涉摸女議員　黨友辯稱：以為係男人","createTime":"2019-04-27T09:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T12:38:03.000Z","uid":225846,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05dae99d93e1242478dd12ef93bb11e8c1f989af","tid":1127690,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427141554071-0427_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190427150701\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427141554071-0427_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190427150701&h=f98f2968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林利子（左小圈）批評文喜相（右小圈）捧臉是性騷擾。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n南韓國會早前爆發衝突，自由韓國黨的議員前往國會議長文喜相的辦公室抗議，爭執之間文喜相疑性騷擾一名女議員。他致歉後突然暈倒，其黨友辯稱「他誤會該女議員是男子」，言論引起批評。自由韓國黨周五（26日）向檢察機關控告文喜相。 <br />\n<br />\n國會周三（24日）因選舉法而爆發衝突，有自由韓國黨議員指控，抗議期間文喜相伸出雙手，觸摸女議員林利子的腹部。當林利子批評「這是性騷擾」後，文喜相改用手捧起她的臉，又雙手擁抱她。 <br />\n<br />\n文喜相其後道歉，表示當時打算離開現場，未想到會不小心有肢體接觸，他疑因承受壓力血糖低暈倒入院；林利子表明不會接受道歉，自己亦因精神受打擊而入院。與文喜相同屬共同民主黨的薛勳為對方護航稱：「<span style=\"color: red;\">以為林利子是男人，才會有相關舉動</span>。」其回應引起批評，輿論要求他辭職謝罪。 <br />\n<br />\n林利子周五到大檢察廳，以涉嫌強制猥褻及侮辱等罪名控告文喜相，表示將追究他的法律責任，所屬黨亦打算向國會倫理委員會投訴。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427141554071-0427_00912_001_02p.jpg?20190427150701\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427141554071-0427_00912_001_02p.jpg%3F20190427150701&h=a1918040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文喜相（紅圈右）涉嫌摸林利子（紅圈左）的腹部。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\non撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbe519ae1af6a79fd2f8f9b52d12397faa5689e","tid":1127690,"uid":114792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"但佢對男人做呢個動作唔係仲詭異咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8349f0d3f8493a211aa8de25d3a9ad71b095e031","tid":1127690,"uid":189911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tam1sgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftam1sgO.jpg&h=ffc070d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97309821e9740889705861bd456c84d104773526","tid":1127690,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294a5729c28a3c7f9c89782386da0b5874cfb853","tid":1127690,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8349f0d3f8493a211aa8de25d3a9ad71b095e031","tid":1127690,"uid":189911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tam1sgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftam1sgO.jpg&h=ffc070d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/swoYmTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FswoYmTx.jpg&h=29105ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}